  "texts": [
    "So, in the first step, we implemented three types of LSTM, Gru, and Bilstm networks with single-cell structures in three single-layer, two-layers, and three-layer architectures.",
    "The aim is to investigate the effect of the number of layers in the structure of the recommender model.",
    "As you can see in Table 4, the results are not desirable.",
    "None of the 9 single-cell architectures has been able to find the pattern and the relationship between different features and their relationship in combination and fitting with different models.",
    "Even increasing the number of layers did not play an essential role in improving the results, and the decrease in the accuracy of the 3-layered model compared to the single-layered model shows that the model is moving toward overfitting."
  ]
}